    Version and name of the CorDapp hosting the other side of the flow.

    • Constructor Detail

      • FlowInfo

        public FlowInfo(int flowVersion,
                @NotNull
                java.lang.String appName)

        Version and name of the CorDapp hosting the other side of the flow.

        Parameters:
        flowVersion - The integer flow version the other side is using.
        appName - Name of the CorDapp jar hosting the flow, without the .jar extension. It will include a unique identifierto deduplicate it from other releases of the same CorDapp, typically a version string. See theCorDapp JAR format for more details.
